1) About The System
####################
This system is to monitor any database based system , and also
it have the avilability to be used as a notification tool that
can send different types of notifications 


what can it do ?
- run queries and send the output via different channels
- run scripts and send the output via different channels

channels:
- mail (html based body)
- mail (text based body)
- mail (with attachement)
- sms
- slack

depandincies:
- Curl (to send to slack)
- mailx (to send via mail)
- sqlplus (to run queries)
