2) Releases
###########
Version 1.0:
-beta version
used to send mail (text based) only , and can only run queries , 
it have its own timer and doesnt depend on crontab

Version 1.1:
-Fixed bugs
added : 
- send mail (html based)
- send mail (with attachement)
- easier to handle

Version 2.0:
- Major release : new code
added :
- send sms

Version 2.1:
- Fixed bugs
added :
- send to slack channels


Version 2.2:
-Fixed bugs

Version 3.0:
Major release : new code
- Different architecture + adding more functions
added :
- CLI commands
all functions now are command based , and no editing in files needed
Please use the command "AMS --help" to understand more

Version 3.1:
- Fixed Minor bugs
added : 
- added more CLI commands (edit|test|log|version)

